column5: Description
PortletRequest artifact is valid during all phases.
ActionRequest artifact is only valid during action phase.
HeaderRequest artifact is only valid during header phase.
RenderRequest artifact is only valid during render phase.
EventRequest artifact is only valid during event phase.
ResourceRequest artifact is only valid during resource phase.
ClientDataRequest artifact is only valid during action and resource phase.
PortletResponse artifact is valid during all phases.
ActionResponse artifact is only valid during action phase.
HeaderResponse artifact is only valid during header phase.
RenderResponse artifact is only valid during render phase.
EventResponse artifact is only valid during event phase.
ResourceResponse artifact is only valid during resource phase.
StateAwareResponse artifact is only valid during action and event phase.
MimeResponse artifact is only valid during header, render and resource phase.
RenderParameters artifact is only valid during render phase.
MutableRenderParameters artifact is only valid during action and event phase.
ActionParameters artifact is only valid during action phase.
ResourceParameters artifact is only valid during resource phase.
PortletConfig artifact is valid during all phases.
PortletContext artifact is valid during all phases.
PortletMode artifact is valid during all phases.
WindowState artifact is valid during all phases.
PortletPreferences artifact is valid during all phases.
Cookies artifact is valid during all phases.
PortletSession artifact is valid during all phases.
Locale artifact is only valid during render and resource phase.
Locales artifact is valid during all phases.
Namespace artifact is valid during all phases.
ContextPath artifact is valid during all phases.
WindowID artifact is valid during all phases.
PortletName artifact is valid during all phases.
